      <h1>ETSI EN 304 223: Baseline Cybersecurity Requirements for AI Models and Systems</h1>
      <p>The first European Standard to address AI-specific cyber threats across the full lifecycle — what it covers, who it applies to, and how to achieve conformity.</p>
